CatDescriptText: Image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 11, 1957, pg. A20, with text reading: "Grand Opening - Jana's a Rendevous [sic] for Discriminating People - New Modern Equipment - Bring Outdoors in Patio Style - Gay Calypso Wall Will Warrant Your Many Glances - John and Pauline Omodio Proudly Announce the Opening of Their New Bar & Lounge located at 1250 Pennsylvania Ave., North Side - Wednesday May 15 - Surprise Entertainment on Opening Night."
TitMainTitle: Jana's bar and lounge with booths, brick wall, and bar in foreground, 1250 Pennsylvania Avenue, Northside
